<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.3">
<l>iṇṭai yāyiṉa koṇṭu toṇṭarka ḷēttu vāruṟa</l>
<l>vōṭum vāṉiṭaik</l>
<l>koṇṭu pōyiṭa vuma tukaṇṭeṉ neñcamaṉpāy</l>
<l>vaṇṭu vāḻvaṭa vēṅka ṭamalai kōyil koṇṭata</l>
<l>ṉōṭum mīmicai</l>
<l>yaṇṭa māṇṭirup pāṟka ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O My companion heart, having seen that [he] truly takes into heaven</l>
<l>Devotees bringing garlands, those who praise [him], and their relatives,</l>
<l>Today you assumed the duty of service to him who sits ruling</l>
<l rend="indent">the highest heaven</l>
<l>And has a temple on northern Vēṅkaṭa Mountain where bees flourish.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
